Thanks bdox, much appreciated.  The guy I usually fish with finished 42nd on day two.  Rice is usually good to me as we won this event in `05 and finished second to Jarrod and Gerrard in `07 by less than a poker chip. Moving into a new house prevented fishing the event for me this year....can you believe the wife wanted me present on moving day, the nerve.  Cheers,  Davo
